<p>I have a table which's content is displayed at listbox. I want to delete rows that user has selected. How to know which rows to delete and how delete?</p>  <p>This is how I display listbox items:</p>  <pre><code>DataSet AllPairs = new DataSet(); AllPairs.ReadXml(PathToPairsXML); listBox1.DataSource = AllPairs.Tables[0]; listBox1.ValueMember = "PAIR_text"; listBox1.DisplayMember = "PAIR_text"; </code></pre>  <p>Listbox selection property is MultiExtended.</p>